&nbsp;

Education

B.A.,&nbsp;EastChinaNormalUniversity,1984.
M.A.,&nbsp;EastChinaNormalUniversity,1987.
Ph.D.,Fudan&nbsp;University,1990.


Experience

Professor,ZhejiangUniversity,1996&mdash;.
Visiting&nbsp;Professor,&nbsp;KyushuUniversity,1994&mdash;1995.
AssociateProfessor,ZhejiangUniversity,1993&mdash;1996.
Lecturer,ZhejiangUniversity,1990&mdash;1993.

Teaching&nbsp;

CoursesforUndergraduates:DifferentialGeometry,DifferentiableManifolds,AnalyticGeometry,HigherAlgebra,Seminar&nbsp;onModernMathematicsI,II.
CoursesforGraduates:GlobalDifferentialGeometry,GeometricAnalysis,&nbsp;CurvatureFlowinGeometry,&nbsp;GlobalGeometryofSubmanifolds,Global&nbsp;RiemannianGeometry,&nbsp;DifferentiableManifoldsandGeometry&nbsp;ofManifolds.&nbsp;




ResearchInterest

GlobalDifferentialGeometry
GeometricAnalysis
TopologyofManifolds



